Indicating a right turn (into Morval Road) for LCN25
This marking seems to pre-date the adjacent shared-use footway designation. Very faded in 2021.
Although turning right from here is permitted, due to the angle of the junction, the traffic lights on the adjoining road, and passing traffic, I would say it is ill-advised.
